const routes = (app) => {
    app.route('/contact')
        .get((req,res) =>
        res.send('GET request successfull'))
           
        .post((req,res) =>
        res.send('POST request succesful'))

    app.route('/contact/:contactID')
        .put((req,res) =>
        res.send('PUT request succesful'))

        .delete((req,res) =>
        res.send('DELETE request succesful'))
}
